Reasoning: The paper deals with the wireless channel characteristics of 5G communications and proposes a fading model that incorporates multiple specular components with clusterized diffuse scattered waves. This topic falls under the domain of information theory (cs.IT), networking and internet architecture (cs.NI), communication and security (cs.COMM), systems and control (cs.SY), and multimedia (cs.MM).
